  <!-- How the NCRS Works -->
  <section class="about-section about-inner">
    <div class="about-section-label">How It Works</div>
    <h2 class="about-section-title">The six dimensions of norm change readiness</h2>
    <div class="about-dim-grid">
      <div class="about-dim-card">
        <span class="about-dim-icon">🎯</span>
        <div class="about-dim-name">Tipping Threshold</div>
        <p class="about-dim-desc">How entrenched is the current norm? Low threshold = easier to tip. Research shows ~35% active participation triggers cascading change.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-dim-card">
        <span class="about-dim-icon">🔒</span>
